DOC.brief_summary: The present study aim explore effect novel multidisciplinary non-pharmacological intervention design improve health parameter well-being overweight obese woman . The propose program health- quality life-oriented , without focus weight loss , follow philosophical principle `` Health Every Size '' , may provide alternative mode intervention traditional one , focus concept `` weight loss cost '' . To evaluate efficacy intervention , mixed-method design combine qualitative quantitative assessment apply .
